item.title: CVE-2020-4485|2024-09-16T22:35:28.004Z -- ibm -- qradar%20wincollect
item.description: IBM QRadar 7.2.0 through 7.2.9 could allow an authenticated user to disable the Wincollect service which could aid an attacker in bypassing security mechanisms in future attacks. IBM X-Force ID: 181860.
